- Mobility provides passenger and freight transportation, such as vehicles, trams and light rail, and commuter trains, as well as trains and passenger coaches; locomotives for freight or passenger transport as well as solutions for automated transportation; products and solutions for rail automation; electrification products; and intermodal solutions.

- SHS develops, manufactures, and sells various diagnostic and therapeutic products and services; and provides clinical consulting services.

- Siemens Financial Services offers leasing, lending, and working capital financing solutions and equipment, project, and structured financing solutions.